[Amit Varma]: why prostitution should be legalized. Block has a chapter on that. Block was a

00:02:27.160 --> 00:02:31.840
[Amit Varma]: libertarian and my guest on the show today is the first libertarian I met in

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:37.600
